<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Subscription Expiring Soon - FinMitra</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body,
        html {
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            width: 100% !important;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f7fa; color: #1e293b; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; line-height: 1.5; width: 100% !important;">
    <div
        style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 16px; background-color: #f5f7fa; -webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <div
            style="width: 100%; max-width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); -webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <div>
                <div align="center" style="padding-bottom:16px;">
                    <img src={{logo}} alt="logo" style="width: 100%; height: auto;" />
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2
                style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; color: #0f172a; margin: 0 0 16px 0; line-height: 1.3;">
                Your Subscription is Expiring Soon</h2>

            <p
                style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #475569; margin: 0 0 24px 0; text-align: center; padding: 0 5px;">
                Dear {{agentName}}, your FinMitra subscription will expire in <strong>{{daysUntilExpiry}} days</strong>
                on {{expiryDate}}.
            </p>

            <div
                style="background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 0 auto 24px; text-align: center; width: 100%; max-width: 300px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
                    <span style="color: #64748b; display: block; font-size: 14px;">Current Plan</span>
                    <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; font-size: 18px;">{{subscriptionPlan}}</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span style="color: #64748b; display: block; font-size: 14px;">Expires On</span>
                    <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #dc2626; font-size: 18px;">{{expiryDate}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                <a href="{{renewalLink}}"
                    style="display: inline-block; background-color: #2563eb; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 auto; -webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">
                    Renew Subscription
                </a>
            </div>

            <div
                style="background-color: #f0f9ff; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #0369a1; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5;">
                    <strong>Note:</strong> Renew now to avoid any interruption in your service. All your data and
                    settings will be preserved.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 20px; text-align: center;">
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; margin: 0 0 8px 0; line-height: 1.4;">If you have any
                    questions about your subscription, please contact our support team.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0; line-height: 1.4;">© {{currentYear}} Altis Infonet
                    Pvt. Ltd. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>